Camille Winbush https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Camille_Winbush 0 Camille Winbush is an American television actress, comedian, and recording artist. Her work in television has earned her three Image Awards and a Young Artist Award. She is best known for her role as Vanessa Thomkins on The Bernie Mac Show.
